<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Home</title>
    <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="data:image/svg+xml,<svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' viewBox='0 0 32 32'><rect width='32' height='32' rx='8' fill='%233d52ff'/><path d='M8 10c0-1.1.9-2 2-2h4l2 2h6a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v8a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H10a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V10z' fill='white'/></svg>">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Geist:wght@400;500;600;700;800;900&family=Inter:wght@300;400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

        :root {
            --bg:             #0e0f13;
            --surface:        #16181f;
            --border:         #2a2d38;
            --blue:           #3d52ff;
            --blue-glow:      rgba(61,82,255,0.25);
            --blue-dim:       rgba(61,82,255,0.12);
            --white:          #f0f1f5;
            --muted:          #6b7080;
            --success:        #22c55e;
            --success-dim:    rgba(34,197,94,0.12);
            --success-border: rgba(34,197,94,0.35);
            --error:          #ef4444;
            --error-dim:      rgba(239,68,68,0.12);
            --error-border:   rgba(239,68,68,0.35);
        }

        html, body { height: 100%; background: var(--bg); color: var(--white); font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; }

        body::before {
            content: ''; position: fixed; inset: 0;
            background-image: linear-gradient(var(--border) 1px, transparent 1px), linear-gradient(90deg, var(--border) 1px, transparent 1px);
            background-size: 48px 48px; opacity: 0.35; pointer-events: none; z-index: 0;
        }
        body::after {
            content: ''; position: fixed; top: -120px; left: -120px; width: 520px; height: 520px;
            background: radial-gradient(circle, var(--blue-glow) 0%, transparent 70%); pointer-events: none; z-index: 0;
        }

        /* ── toast ── */
        .toast {
            position: fixed; top: 16px; left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%) translateY(-12px); z-index: 9999;
            display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px;
            padding: 11px 16px; border-radius: 10px;
            font-family: 'Geist', sans-serif; font-size: 0.85rem; font-weight: 500;
            backdrop-filter: blur(12px); box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0,0,0,0.4);
            opacity: 0; animation: toastIn .35s ease forwards, toastOut .35s ease 4s forwards;
            max-width: calc(100vw - 32px); white-space: normal; word-break: break-word;
        }
        .toast.success { background: var(--success-dim); border: 1px solid var(--success-border); color: #86efac; }
        .toast.error   { background: var(--error-dim);   border: 1px solid var(--error-border);   color: #fca5a5; }
        .toast-icon { width: 18px; height: 18px; border-radius: 50%; display: grid; place-items: center; flex-shrink: 0; }
        .toast.success .toast-icon { background: var(--success); }
        .toast.error   .toast-icon { background: var(--error); }
        .toast-icon svg { width: 10px; height: 10px; stroke: #fff; fill: none; stroke-width: 2.5; }
        .toast-close { margin-left: 8px; cursor: pointer; opacity: 0.6; transition: opacity .15s; background: none; border: none; color: inherit; padding: 4px; line-height: 1; flex-shrink: 0; }
        .toast-close:hover { opacity: 1; }
        .toast-close svg { width: 12px; height: 12px; stroke: currentColor; fill: none; stroke-width: 2; }
        @keyframes toastIn  { from { opacity: 0; transform: translateX(-50%) translateY(-12px); } to { opacity: 1; transform: translateX(-50%) translateY(0); } }
        @keyframes toastOut { from { opacity: 1; transform: translateX(-50%) translateY(0); } to { opacity: 0; transform: translateX(-50%) translateY(-12px); } }

        /* ── nav ── */
        nav {
            position: relative; z-index: 100;
            display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;
            padding: 0 48px; height: 68px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px); background: rgba(14,15,19,0.9);
        }
        .nav-logo { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; font-family: 'Geist', sans-serif; font-weight: 800; font-size: 1.2rem; color: var(--white); text-decoration: none; }
        .nav-logo-icon { width: 34px; height: 34px; background: var(--blue); border-radius: 8px; display: grid; place-items: center; flex-shrink: 0; }
        .nav-logo-icon svg { width: 18px; height: 18px; fill: #fff; }
        .nav-links { display: flex; gap: 36px; list-style: none; }
        .nav-links a { font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--muted); text-decoration: none; transition: color .2s; }
        .nav-links a:hover { color: var(--white); }
        .nav-cta { padding: 8px 22px; border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 6px; color: var(--white); text-decoration: none; font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: 500; transition: border-color .2s, background .2s; white-space: nowrap; }
        .nav-cta:hover { border-color: var(--blue); background: var(--blue-dim); }

        /* hamburger */
        .nav-hamburger { display: none; flex-direction: column; gap: 5px; cursor: pointer; padding: 4px; background: none; border: none; }
        .nav-hamburger span { display: block; width: 22px; height: 2px; background: var(--white); border-radius: 2px; transition: all .25s; }
        .nav-hamburger.open span:nth-child(1) { transform: translateY(7px) rotate(45deg); }
        .nav-hamburger.open span:nth-child(2) { opacity: 0; }
        .nav-hamburger.open span:nth-child(3) { transform: translateY(-7px) rotate(-45deg); }

        .nav-mobile-menu {
            display: none; position: fixed; top: 68px; left: 0; right: 0;
            background: rgba(14,15,19,0.98); backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); z-index: 99;
            padding: 20px 24px; flex-direction: column; gap: 4px;
        }
        .nav-mobile-menu.open { display: flex; }
        .nav-mobile-menu a { color: var(--muted); text-decoration: none; font-size: 1rem; padding: 12px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); transition: color .2s; }
        .nav-mobile-menu a:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
        .nav-mobile-menu a:hover, .nav-mobile-menu a.active { color: var(--white); }
        .nav-mobile-cta { margin-top: 8px; padding: 12px; background: var(--blue); color: #fff !important; border-radius: 8px; text-align: center; font-weight: 600; border-bottom: none !important; }

        /* ── main ── */
        main { position: relative; z-index: 1; max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 80px 48px; }

        /* ── hero ── */
        .hero-label {
            display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;
            background: var(--blue-dim); border: 1px solid rgba(61,82,255,0.3);
            border-radius: 99px; padding: 5px 14px;
            font-size: 0.75rem; color: #8b9bff; letter-spacing: 0.08em; text-transform: uppercase;
            margin-bottom: 28px; animation: fadeUp .5s ease both;
        }
        .hero-label span { width: 6px; height: 6px; background: var(--blue); border-radius: 50%; flex-shrink: 0; }
        h1 { font-family: 'Geist', sans-serif; font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3.8rem); font-weight: 800; line-height: 1.1; letter-spacing: -0.02em; margin-bottom: 18px; animation: fadeUp .55s .08s ease both; }
        h1 span { color: var(--blue); }
        .hero-sub { font-size: 1rem; color: var(--muted); max-width: 460px; line-height: 1.65; margin-bottom: 48px; animation: fadeUp .55s .14s ease both; }

        /* ── ID card ── */
        .id-card { background: rgba(34,197,94,0.07); border: 1px solid rgba(34,197,94,0.3); border-radius: 12px; padding: 20px 24px; margin-bottom: 48px; animation: fadeUp .4s ease both; }
        .id-card-header { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; font-family: 'Geist', sans-serif; font-weight: 700; font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--success); text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.06em; margin-bottom: 12px; }
        .id-card-header svg { width: 16px; height: 16px; stroke: var(--success); fill: none; stroke-width: 2.5; flex-shrink: 0; }
        .id-value-wrap { display: flex; align-items: stretch; gap: 10px; margin-bottom: 12px; }
        .id-value { flex: 1; font-family: 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 0.95rem; color: var(--white); background: rgba(0,0,0,0.35); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 8px; padding: 12px 16px; word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0.04em; min-width: 0; }
        .copy-btn { flex-shrink: 0; width: 42px; min-height: 42px; background: rgba(0,0,0,0.3); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 8px; display: grid; place-items: center; cursor: pointer; transition: border-color .2s, background .2s; color: var(--muted); }
        .copy-btn:hover  { border-color: var(--blue);    background: var(--blue-dim);    color: var(--blue); }
        .copy-btn.copied { border-color: var(--success); background: var(--success-dim); color: var(--success); }
        .copy-btn svg { width: 16px; height: 16px; stroke: currentColor; fill: none; stroke-width: 2; }
        .id-expiry { font-size: 0.82rem; color: var(--error); line-height: 1.5; margin-top: 10px; }
        .id-expiry strong { color: #ff8080; font-weight: 600; }

        /* ── action cards ── */
        .action-cards { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 20px; animation: fadeUp .55s .2s ease both; margin-bottom: 64px; }
        .card { background: var(--surface); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 14px; padding: 28px 24px; text-decoration: none; color: inherit; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 14px; transition: border-color .25s, transform .25s, box-shadow .25s; }
        .card:hover { border-color: var(--blue); transform: translateY(-3px); box-shadow: 0 12px 40px var(--blue-glow); }
        .card-icon { width: 44px; height: 44px; background: var(--blue-dim); border: 1px solid rgba(61,82,255,0.25); border-radius: 10px; display: grid; place-items: center; flex-shrink: 0; }
        .card-icon svg { width: 20px; height: 20px; stroke: var(--blue); fill: none; stroke-width: 1.8; }
        .card-title { font-family: 'Geist', sans-serif; font-weight: 700; font-size: 1.1rem; }
        .card-desc { font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.6; }
        .card-arrow { margin-top: auto; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px; font-size: 0.825rem; font-weight: 500; color: var(--blue); }
        .card-arrow svg { width: 14px; height: 14px; stroke: var(--blue); fill: none; stroke-width: 2; transition: transform .2s; flex-shrink: 0; }
        .card:hover .card-arrow svg { transform: translateX(4px); }

        /* ── features ── */
        .section-label { font-size: 0.75rem; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: var(--muted); margin-bottom: 12px; animation: fadeUp .5s .3s ease both; }
        .section-title { font-family: 'Geist', sans-serif; font-size: clamp(1.4rem, 3vw, 1.75rem); font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 8px; animation: fadeUp .5s .35s ease both; }
        .section-sub   { font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--muted); margin-bottom: 36px; animation: fadeUp .5s .4s ease both; }
        .feature-grid  { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 16px; animation: fadeUp .55s .42s ease both; }
        .feature-card  { background: var(--surface); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 12px; padding: 22px 20px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 12px; transition: border-color .2s, transform .2s; }
        .feature-card:hover { border-color: rgba(61,82,255,0.4); transform: translateY(-2px); }
        .feature-icon  { width: 38px; height: 38px; background: var(--blue-dim); border: 1px solid rgba(61,82,255,0.2); border-radius: 9px; display: grid; place-items: center; flex-shrink: 0; }
        .feature-icon svg { width: 18px; height: 18px; stroke: var(--blue); fill: none; stroke-width: 1.8; }
        .feature-title { font-family: 'Geist', sans-serif; font-weight: 600; font-size: 0.92rem; }
        .feature-desc  { font-size: 0.82rem; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.6; }

        /* ── footer ── */
        footer { position: relative; z-index: 1; border-top: 1px solid var(--border); padding: 22px 48px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--muted); flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 12px; }
        footer a { color: var(--muted); text-decoration: none; transition: color .2s; }
        footer a:hover { color: var(--white); }
        .footer-right { display: flex; gap: 20px; align-items: center; flex-wrap: wrap; }
        .footer-email  { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px; }
        .footer-email svg { width: 14px; height: 14px; stroke: currentColor; fill: none; stroke-width: 1.8; }

        @keyframes fadeUp { from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(18px); } to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); } }

        /* ── RESPONSIVE ── */

        /* Tablet landscape */
        @media (max-width: 1024px) {
            nav { padding: 0 32px; }
            main { padding: 60px 32px; }
            footer { padding: 20px 32px; }
            .feature-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
        }

        /* Tablet portrait */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            nav { padding: 0 20px; }
            .nav-links, .nav-cta { display: none; }
            .nav-hamburger { display: flex; }
            main { padding: 48px 20px 60px; }
            h1 { font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 6vw, 2.6rem); }
            .hero-sub { font-size: 0.95rem; margin-bottom: 36px; }
            .action-cards { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 14px; margin-bottom: 48px; }
            .card { padding: 22px 18px; gap: 12px; }
            .card-title { font-size: 1rem; }
            .card-desc { font-size: 0.825rem; }
            footer { padding: 18px 20px; flex-direction: column; align-items: flex-start; gap: 10px; }
            .footer-right { gap: 16px; }
        }

        /* Phone large */
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .feature-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
            .action-cards { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
            .id-value { font-size: 0.82rem; padding: 10px 12px; letter-spacing: 0.02em; }
        }

        /* Phone small */
        @media (max-width: 400px) {
            .nav-logo span { display: none; }
            h1 { font-size: 1.7rem; }
            .hero-label { font-size: 0.7rem; }
            .id-card { padding: 16px; }
            .copy-btn { width: 36px; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <% if (locals.message && !locals.id) { %>
        <% const isError = locals.message.toLowerCase().includes('error') || locals.message.toLowerCase().includes('fail') || locals.message.toLowerCase().includes('invalid') || locals.message.toLowerCase().includes('not '); %>
        <% const toastType = isError ? 'error' : 'success'; %>
        <div class="toast <%= toastType %>" id="toast">
            <div class="toast-icon">
                <% if (toastType === 'success') { %><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
                <% } else { %><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><line x1="18" y1="6" x2="6" y2="18"/><line x1="6" y1="6" x2="18" y2="18"/></svg><% } %>
            </div>
            <%= locals.message %>
            <button class="toast-close" onclick="dismissToast()"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><line x1="18" y1="6" x2="6" y2="18"/><line x1="6" y1="6" x2="18" y2="18"/></svg></button>
        </div>
    <% } %>

    <nav>
        <a href="/" class="nav-logo">
            <div class="nav-logo-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M3 7c0-1.1.9-2 2-2h4l2 2h8a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v8a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V7z"/></svg></div>
            <span>FileVault</span>
        </a>
        <ul class="nav-links">
            <li><a href="/">Home</a></li>
            <li><a href="/upload">Upload</a></li>
            <li><a href="/download">Download</a></li>
        </ul>
        <a href="/upload" class="nav-cta">Get Started</a>
        <button class="nav-hamburger" id="hamburger" aria-label="Menu">
            <span></span><span></span><span></span>
        </button>
    </nav>

    <div class="nav-mobile-menu" id="mobileMenu">
        <a href="/">Home</a>
        <a href="/upload">Upload</a>
        <a href="/download">Download</a>
        <a href="/upload" class="nav-mobile-cta">Get Started</a>
    </div>

    <main>
        <div class="hero-label"><span></span> Secure File Storage</div>
        <h1>Store your files.<br><span>Access them anywhere.</span></h1>
        <p class="hero-sub">Upload any file and get a unique ID. Use that ID anytime to retrieve and download your file — fast, simple, and secure.</p>

        <% if (locals.id) { %>
        <div class="id-card">
            <div class="id-card-header">
                <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
                File Uploaded Successfully
            </div>
            <div class="id-value-wrap">
                <div class="id-value" id="fileId"><%= locals.id %></div>
                <button class="copy-btn" id="copyBtn" onclick="copyId()" title="Copy ID">
                    <svg id="copyIcon" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><rect x="9" y="9" width="13" height="13" rx="2"/><path d="M5 15H4a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V4a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h9a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v1"/></svg>
                </button>
            </div>
            <p class="id-expiry"><strong>Save this ID — it won't be shown again.</strong> This file will be automatically deleted after <strong>15 minutes</strong>.</p>
        </div>
        <% } %>

        <div class="action-cards">
            <a href="/upload" class="card">
                <div class="card-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><polyline points="16 16 12 12 8 16"/><line x1="12" y1="12" x2="12" y2="21"/><path d="M20.39 18.39A5 5 0 0 0 18 9h-1.26A8 8 0 1 0 3 16.3"/></svg></div>
                <div class="card-title">Upload a File</div>
                <div class="card-desc">Choose any file from your device and store it securely. You'll receive a unique ID to retrieve it later.</div>
                <div class="card-arrow">Upload now <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"/><polyline points="12 5 19 12 12 19"/></svg></div>
            </a>
            <a href="/download" class="card">
                <div class="card-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><polyline points="8 17 12 21 16 17"/><line x1="12" y1="12" x2="12" y2="21"/><path d="M20.88 18.09A5 5 0 0 0 18 9h-1.26A8 8 0 1 0 3 16.29"/></svg></div>
                <div class="card-title">Download a File</div>
                <div class="card-desc">Already uploaded? Enter your unique file ID to instantly retrieve and download your file.</div>
                <div class="card-arrow">Download now <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"/><polyline points="12 5 19 12 12 19"/></svg></div>
            </a>
        </div>

        <div class="section-label">Why FileVault</div>
        <div class="section-title">Everything you need, nothing you don't</div>
        <p class="section-sub">Built for simplicity — no accounts, no friction, just upload and retrieve.</p>

        <div class="feature-grid">
            <div class="feature-card">
                <div class="feature-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><rect x="3" y="11" width="18" height="11" rx="2"/><path d="M7 11V7a5 5 0 0 1 10 0v4"/></svg></div>
                <div class="feature-title">No Account Needed</div>
                <div class="feature-desc">Upload instantly without signing up. Just pick a file, hit upload, and your unique ID is ready in seconds.</div>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-card">
                <div class="feature-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><polyline points="16 16 12 12 8 16"/><line x1="12" y1="12" x2="12" y2="21"/><path d="M20.39 18.39A5 5 0 0 0 18 9h-1.26A8 8 0 1 0 3 16.3"/></svg></div>
                <div class="feature-title">Any File Type</div>
                <div class="feature-desc">PDFs, images, videos, ZIPs, documents — FileVault stores any format without conversion or compression.</div>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-card">
                <div class="feature-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71"/><path d="M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71"/></svg></div>
                <div class="feature-title">Shareable by ID</div>
                <div class="feature-desc">Share the file ID with anyone. They can retrieve and download the file from any device, anywhere.</div>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-card">
                <div class="feature-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><polyline points="12 6 12 12 16 14"/></svg></div>
                <div class="feature-title">Instant Retrieval</div>
                <div class="feature-desc">No waiting, no queues. Paste your ID on the download page and your file starts downloading immediately.</div>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-card">
                <div class="feature-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M21 15v4a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-4"/><polyline points="7 10 12 15 17 10"/><line x1="12" y1="15" x2="12" y2="3"/></svg></div>
                <div class="feature-title">Original Filename Preserved</div>
                <div class="feature-desc">Files are downloaded with their original name intact — no garbled strings or renamed files.</div>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-card">
                <div class="feature-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><ellipse cx="12" cy="5" rx="9" ry="3"/><path d="M21 12c0 1.66-4 3-9 3s-9-1.34-9-3"/><path d="M3 5v14c0 1.66 4 3 9 3s9-1.34 9-3V5"/></svg></div>
                <div class="feature-title">Persistent Storage</div>
                <div class="feature-desc">Files are stored securely on disk and tracked in MongoDB — your upload stays available as long as you have the ID.</div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>

    <footer>
        <span>Created by <a href="https://github.com/HumayunSaghir" target="_blank">Humayun Saghir</a></span>
        <div class="footer-right">
            <a href="mailto:hr32967262@gmail.com" class="footer-email">
                <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M4 4h16c1.1 0 2 .9 2 2v12c0 1.1-.9 2-2 2H4c-1.1 0-2-.9-2-2V6c0-1.1.9-2 2-2z"/><polyline points="22,6 12,13 2,6"/></svg>
                hr32967262@gmail.com
            </a>
            <a href="https://github.com/HumayunSaghir" target="_blank">
